data.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* age≤18 years, no gender limitation;
* The ECOG （performance status，PS）is 0～1 score;
* The expected survival time is not less than 12 weeks;
* Heart function: A) Cardiac COLOR ultrasound detection LVEF≥ 50%; B) EKG suggests no myocardial ischemia;C) No history of arrhythmia req
